+
+### Semantic Graph Language (ThinkGraph / KnowGraph)
+- Added first-pass shared semantic graph contracts (frontend + backend v3 types):
+  - `SemanticGraphRecord` (JSON-LD compatible `@context`, `@id`, `@type`)
