+3. Smooth drag updates using localized animation-frame scheduling.
+4. Add right-edge drag threshold to collapse companion/canvas mode to chat-only.
+5. Preserve existing workspace/canvas interaction model.
+6. Run frontend validation scripts.
+7. Report implemented safe 80% and remaining polish items.
